{"type": "article", "id": 30415, "title": "这本纪念册里的公路照片，既好看又好吃｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-01T23:05:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 30907, "name": "NONCENSE"}, {"id": 30908, "name": "AR Designs"}, {"id": 30909, "name": "Memac Ogilvy & Mather"}, {"id": 29996, "name": "Dmitry Kozinenko"}, {"id": 30910, "name": "Taeg Nishimoto"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804171323gKwxP7Rlc8qMTZoX.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Painterly Spectrum by Taeg Nishimoto</h3><p>这些由三个独立部分组成的三角形树脂台灯 Painterly Spectrum 是日本设计师 <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/taegnishimoto\" rel=\"nofollow\">Taeg Nishimoto</a> 的最新作品，点亮之后就像是实体化的彩虹。为了制作出这些五彩的灯罩，Nishimoto 先在羊皮纸上用乳胶漆进行创作，在干燥过程中再将环氧树脂涂在表面。羊皮纸会在完全干燥后移除，留下成型的树脂以及乳胶的独特质感。台灯高约 30 到 40 厘米，厚度仅为 3 毫米，不同颜色组件可以自由组合，白天也可以作为一件漂亮的装饰品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222729u1h2FKNiCw53WlaZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.880196\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222727EXkK8RA0LgW4VBDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684597\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222729aNij5TfcJytHVKBw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222729oHIXK5QFga6nRDcZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.585575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222729LliDv9yfx4ndkhqC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222730WDvGb8TuYoO5RSNd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.370416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>N by NONCENSE</h3><p>谁说线香座不可以变得有趣好玩儿？由澳大利亚一对设计师好友创立的品牌 NONCENSE 最近就以食物作为灵感设计了三款线香座，这些栩栩如生的香蕉、披萨和煎蛋均由手工打造而成。每款线香座都随印有品牌 logo 的木盒寄送，还附赠一个黑色的托特包。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.noncense.com.au/products\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 150 澳元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222701QKeB15nzqH9Vb2mU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222701ruVxYPLKk1OEnhWZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222701l0fvAu62CQnsKTFW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222701GrQ75l06cJomyzLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222701MKolmAN0YLqdGE6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222701Sm5MsdIBLVGUWNxQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>OvRcharge by AR Designs</h3><p>无线充电已经不再稀奇了，AR Designs 推出的 OvRcharge 选择在充电“姿势”上下功夫，为充电设备增加了悬浮功能。为了实现悬浮的效果，使用时需要安装配套的超薄手机壳或者 7 毫米厚的适配器，两者均内置了电力感应接收器和磁铁。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/261307172/ovrcharge-levitating-wireless-charger\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 229 加元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222542jCTgGNbfPVW6MhRF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.627941\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222543D8CEF5RYfk0Mt9pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222543jBolNRHOqdpV4ZeX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222543WkoUNZPETxmrF1ua.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222543zqOTSn6wuAJMe2Q4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Field by Dmitry Kozinenko</h3><p>想要创造独特的视觉效果并不一定需要特别复杂的设计，这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/32458529/Field\" rel=\"nofollow\">Field</a> 的极简架子就是一个典型的案例。它由来自乌克兰的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/Dimas1c\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dmitry Kozinenko</a> 设计，我们曾经介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29376.html\">海胆柜</a>也是他的作品。整个架子由黑色或白色的金属框架构成，Kozinenko 在当中对五处金属管进行了弯折处理，可以作为搁板放上物品。从正面远远看去物品就好像是漂浮在空中一样，走近后又像是一个神奇的金属瀑布。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222442ybo678gCs2zpr5Oc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222444QifN3opR2SHr4Xmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608012224437zq9CyA2trlWDQLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222444aWnwFRir6m43I0go.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801222445URPlGQBiLH2bknoI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608012224437KWir5I2lfohkZRP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Eat the Road by Memac Ogilvy &amp; Mather</h3><p>为了庆祝 GTI 问世 40 周年，大众汽车委托<a href=\"http://ogilvy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">奥美</a>中东地区分公司设计了一个特别的纪念品，从它的名字 Eat the Road 中就能猜出个大概：你不仅可以在这本书中看到来自世界各地的公路风光，还能品尝到各种口味的巧克力。书中收录了一系列高质量的相片，作为普通的相片书放在桌上欣赏本身就是一个不错的选择。每一张相片上公路的部分都是拥有特殊风味的巧克力，可以撕下来直接食用。这种既能看又能吃的创意让人不禁联想到《查理和巧克力工厂》中旺卡巧克力工厂生产的可以舔的墙纸，既有趣又充满了未来感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221857oAr3DTRpwPsVaEOv.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221858Zy3cqGrRHBT6Pf1W.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.878000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221856Oyn3pLocC97xhS2K.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.718000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221856Mh4kaodVYywtQm7B.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.843000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221855ogZzdkWMlIJOQLsY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.798667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221855YLcIE4QifAxsaneW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Brum Box by Toms Grinbergs &amp; Aldis Blicsons</h3><p>自行车包装并非只有被丢进垃圾桶的命运，当你看到这个名为 Brum Box 的纸板自行车架时或许会觉得它才是主角产品。在 Toms Grinbergs 和 Aldis Blicsons 联手设计了木制儿童自行车 Brum Brum 之后，他们决定为它打造一个实用而且有趣的外包装。考虑到目标受众是 2 到 6 岁的孩子，设计师们沿着包装画上了小房子和车库的图案。Brum Box 就像是一个手工玩具，只需要简单的折叠，小骑手们就轻松地把它组装起来，还能够为图案添上颜色。这是自行车的<a href=\"http://www.brumbrum.me/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 299 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221827yuUIJ4sZjCH5YAef.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221828TVBhmjsy0EGqikPv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.826250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221828sX95U1ix3Noe4lwy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221827to5BgbOMT98RFvVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221828o3ymjqnsArd9G4Vl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801221827vZtTLdhWJzmOaU3I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}